mts.s: The In4maniacs core business objective is to provide the Informatics students at the University of California, Irvine a better website covering all information with regards to the Informatics Department. The In4maniacs will be redesigning the UCI’s Informatics website by organizing information that is easily navigated and placing information in correct sections. This will alleviate the confusion of information and students can easily come back and locate specific information they need. In addition to organizing, the team plans to change the interface such that there are more visual presentations in which the Informatics can further promote its major. Also, the redesigning will bring the website up-to-date aesthetically and promote itself more to current students and future students alike. This project will reduce internal costs by using more up-to-date, cost-effective tools to build and maintain the website.
